OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells with the odd
OL,6,Fshower at first this morning. Rain
OL,7,Fwill spread north across Orkney from
OL,8,Flate morning becoming patchy as it
OL,9,Freaches Shetland late in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Fresh southeast wind
OL,11,Fstrengthens later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPatchy rain during the
OL,14,Fevening will become more widespread
OL,15,Ffrom the late evening. Orkney will see
OL,16,Fthe best of any dry spells towards the
OL,17,Fmorning. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
