OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FRain will clear from the south
OL,6,Fduring the morning leaving bright
OL,7,Fspells with a few showers until the
OL,8,Flate afternoon when showery rain
OL,9,Fspreads east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FEarly
OL,12,Fshowers clear Shetland Tuesday morning
OL,13,Fleaving the Isles dry with sunny
OL,14,Fspells until early Thursday. Outbreaks
OL,15,Fof rain spread east over the Isles
OL,16,Ffrom Thursday afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
